data_array.en_us:
Set the duration of play (the length of a single play).
If the duration is longer than the audio length, you need to wait for the remaining duration after the audio is complete;
If the duration is shorter than the audio length, the audio will stop or loop when it is not complete.

According to the classification of Kardashev civilization level:
First-class civilization can develop and utilize all the resources of the planet on which it inhabits;
Secondary civilization can collect the energy of the entire star system and even allow the matter to break the speed limit of light;
Third level civilization can master and use all the energy of the entire galaxy.

<color="#FD965ECC">Possessing the ability to build a Dyson sphere indicates that humanity will move towards the Secondary civilization.</color>

